	   <tr><td colspan=2>Hey there i have a Ikkie BL and thought i'd add my 2cp's worth. 32 onwards was DSM with kei i took the whole of the shroom castle camp and lvl'd super quick there. maybe an hour per lvl or a bit more. but then you'd know that lvlling other chars there.<br><br>also good exp is TD with the Ogre camp there, dont know what it is like with 30 lvl's since i came there at 43 but it is great for us.<br><br>if you can get a good enough grp try out ToFS since i went there with a mate and got to 41 easy peasy. although did have a 59cleric for the PLing. but have gone back since to get the keys for myself and the lower lvl's should be good for the high 30's. then its back to TD from 40ish to hunt spirocs which are the camp just behind the ogre camp previously mentioned. and that should see you into your 50's no problem. once you got 50 the world is your oyster, and as mentioned this class is seriously going places and rocks from 40 onwards. after 50 raids will be your main exp i think with grp's in Sebilis and UP and PoG and they all drop good beasty gear.<br><br>and dont forget to use your flash of light spell. it is great to fear kite with at lower lvls and also helps if you are in a sticky getting pwnage from a mob and sow has gone. hope this all helps<br>&nbsp;<br>Tassoth Bonestripper.<br>IKSAR MONK 55th lvl<br>I know what I AM, But What are YOU!!</td></tr>
