	   <tr><td colspan=2>DEX is useful since it helps make your offensive skills climb faster. AGI does the same for defensive skills.&nbsp;&nbsp;DEX also allows weapons that can to proc more frequently.  You are a WIS caster so push WIS is my advice.  You need the mana for buffs and heals for the warder.  If you have some left over for others in the party, wonderful.<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
